manifest.label: Simple
manifest.author: Esri R&D Center Beijing
manifest.description: This is a barebones, simple widget. It includes an example of how to use the config file, and it includes a placeholder SVG icon. It intentionally does not include the following so you can use this to start from scratch: i18n translations, a Settings panel, unit tests. See the documentation for more information on how to implement these features.
